"Drift with bins in accelerating cavity: create significant energy spread that leads to multiple bins. When particles are close to c, bin number decreases."
stat "rms_x" last 1E-3
stat "rms_y" last 1E-3
stat "rms_s" last 1E-2
stat "rms_px" last 1E-3
stat "rms_py" last 1E-3
stat "rms_ps" last 1E-2
stat "energy" last 1E3
stat "nBins" avg 0.2
